본 lean4 formal verification roadmap 의 main work scope 가 hexa-bio 의 신규 약물 (de novo drug) lifecycle 안에서 formal verification representative role 로 reframe. 기존 F-CL-FORMAL-* axes (1-4) WEAVE composition algebra 는 canonical 보존; novel drug context 의 formal verification scope 추가.

cross-link:
- `.roadmap.novel_drugs` — de novo drug list
- `.roadmap.meta_novel_drugs` — 5-axis + 6-stage lifecycle
- `.roadmap.weave` — WEAVE composition algebra (lean4 single source of truth)

### Novel drug formal verification scope

novel drug lifecycle 의 formal verification 가능 부분:
- **Stage 1 Design**: SMILES → 3D conformer 의 RDKit determinism (ETKDGv3+UFF seed reproducibility)
- **Stage 2 Quantum VQE**: ParityMapper Z2 tapering 의 algebraic preservation (lean4 group-theoretic proof)
- **Stage 3 Delivery**: WEAVE scaffold composition 의 lean4 axes 1-4 (existing formal track)
- **Stage 5 Disease phenotype**: σ(6)=12 / τ(6)=4 / φ(6)=2 / J₂(6)=24 invariant 의 lean4 mechanical proof
- **Stage 6 Ranking**: Spearman correlation algebraic property

본 lean4 track 의 진정한 next ramp = novel drug 의 lifecycle 안에서 axes 1-4 promote 시 5-axis 통합 검증 자동 prerequisite.

raw#10 honest C3:
  - lean4 mechanical proof = real-semantics promotion (axes 2/3/4); novel drug 의 wet-lab efficacy 와는 별도 layer.
  - formal verification 의 scope = WEAVE composition + 5-axis invariant; novel drug binding-affinity 의 quantum chem-acc 자체는 lean4 외부 (PySCF + qiskit-nature 의 numerical verification).
